   Over 24346 sequences were generated in Phase I of this project.

  News Update

     * The ITEC sequences have been deposited to the National Center for
       Biotechnology Information (NCBI, Bethesda, MD) GenBank dbEST
       database
     * The Institute for Genomic Research (TIGR, Rockville, MD) has
       integrated wheat ESTs from public databases (mainly dbEST) and
       displayed them on their TIGR Gene Indices Page. The Wheat Gene
       Index one of several listed there.

